src:
Hasil FP3 Moto2 Malaysia: Brad Binder Asapi Alex Marquez
02 Nov 2019, 09:52 by Bola.net
Bola.net - Pebalap Red Bull KTM Ajo, Brad Binder, sukses mencatat waktu tercepat dalam sesi latihan bebas ketiga (FP3) Moto2 Malaysia di Sirkuit Sepang pada Sabtu (2/11/2019).
Pebalap Afrika Selatan ini diikuti oleh pebalap Estrella Galicia 0,0 Marc VDS, Alex Marquez, di posisi kedua dan pebalap ONEXOX TKKR SAG Team, Tetsuta Nagashima, di posisi ketiga.
Sementara itu posisi keempat dan kelima masing-masing ditempati oleh pebalap ONEXOX TKKR SAG Team lainnya, Remy Gardner, dan pebalap Dynavolt Intact GP, Thomas Luthi.
Berikut hasil FP3 Moto2 Malaysia 2019.
text:
Malaysian Moto3 FP3 Results: Brad Binder Asapi Alex Marquez
02 Nov 2019, 09:52 by Bola.net
Bola.net - Red Bull KTM racer Ajo, Brad Binder, successfully recorded the fastest time in the third free practice session (FP3) Moto2 Malaysia at the Sepang Circuit on Saturday (11/02/2019).
The South African rider was followed by Estrella Galicia 0.0 Marc VDS, Alex Marquez, in second place and ONEXOX TKKR SAG Team, Tetsuta Nagashima, in third.
Meanwhile the fourth and fifth positions were each occupied by other ONEXOX TKKR SAG Team riders, Remy Gardner, and Dynavolt Intact GP rider Thomas Luthi.
Following are the results of FP3 Moto2 Malaysia 2019.
